  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The shaman causes the speed of a creature within 30 feet to be halved. The target can attempt a Fortitude saving throw to negate this effect. The penalty lasts for a number of rounds equal to the shaman’s character level and does not stack with other effects that reduce speed.</p>\n<p>Whether or not the save is successful, the creature can’t be the target of this hex again for 24 hours.</p>"
